# docs/chronicle/

Project Chronicle — pre-compacted development history for AI agent context.

## Structure

- `index.json` — machine-readable epoch index
- `epoch-YYYY-label.md` — one file per epoch (YAML frontmatter + markdown body)

## Purpose

Each agent reads chronicle epochs instead of raw git history, reducing
per-agent context cost from ~50,000 tokens to ~3,000 tokens. Epochs are
generated by the Historian keeper and validated against git history.
